{"id":"48d28de8-0dc1-4e02-a825-eb57772cf11f","name":"Strangers in the woods","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">Riding home from work one day you decided to take a shortcut through some nearby woods... but you can't drive out. The forest doesn't end.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Why are there strange people waving at you?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3lOmWUmWRyZFOYTc9WEX0.webp?width=1000\">_______________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><u>RULES:</u></strong></p><ol><li><p style=\"text-align: justify\"><em>Successfully drive four strange hitch hikers through the woods to their destinations.</em></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: justify\"><em>Repeat the first rule and you'll escape alive.</em></p></li></ol><p style=\"text-align: justify\">_______________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2113bf90-432a-4ebe-b681-899843077697_character-strangers-in-the-woods-male-vers\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(3, 11, 255)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 247); color: inherit\">CLICK HERE FOR AN ALTERNATIVE MALE VERSION OF THIS BOT MEANT FOR THE FEMALE P.O.V</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p>_______________________________________________</p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 35, 255); color: inherit\">The Strange Trilogy [My other horror bot links]</mark></strong></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a4fb2a3b-8c2d-48dc-8790-91199fd6bed7_character-strange-world-remake\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Strange World [Remake]</a></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a107ac1a-7259-44d4-a3c3-abbbd5ff83b4_character-strange-visitors\" rel=\"noopener